1) Download the zip file
2) Unzip
3) go to (click on) bin
4) click on CongruentSearch (windows or Linux) or CongruentSearch.bat (PC)
5) If necessary, authorise installation of this software
6) Open a tab in your browser, and go to (type in) localhost:7000
7) You should see the CongruentSearch screen
8) Click File then Import and upload something (e.g. a pdf or a web-page)
9) Type a query into the blue search box, e.g. "and" and hit return